author: @alaakela
content: Just how unimaginative or creatively bankrupt you have to be as an artist that at 60 you still try to do your old sexy poses? Couldn't to come up with anything new? Something that actually either fits you at age 60 or revolutionary at age 60? Not this pretending to be young and sexy old stuff that neither sexy not revolutionary?
